Step 1. Create Storage Account

Download The Zip File website.zip

Login Azure Console -> Search Bar -> Storage accounts -> Select The Storage accounts -> Create -> Select The Resource group -> Storage account name -> Name -> Go To Review + create Tab -> Create



Step 2. Enable Static Website Hosting

Search Bar -> Storage accounts -> Select The Storage accounts -> Select The Storage account -> Click On Data management On Left menu -> Select The Static website -> Click On Enabled -> Index document name(index.html) -> Save ->



Step 3. Upload Website Files

Click On Data storage On Left menu -> Select The Containers -> Click On $web -> Upload -> Upload All Website Files And Folders 
